news: [Pinned] You use jSQL for CTFs, university study, or security research? Please consider adding a Star to GitHub at https://github.com/ron190/jsql-injection
[Contribute] Injection strategies can be missing or improved even for common engines like SQLite, share your knowledge to improve jSQL
[Strategy DNS] Participate in implementing out-of-band DNS injection with Docker and open a pull request on GitHub
[Benchmark] Enhance the tool usability, use jSQL on challenge platforms like TryHackMe and HackTheBox and report your experience on GitHub
